Description: VETS USA Inc. will give investors the satisfaction of a decent return on investment.
Headquarters Regions: Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: VETS USA Inc. will give investors the satisfaction of a decent return on investment.  The corporation will develop profit by participating with veteran owned businesses by profit sharing and interest on invested funds.  Many vets have gained knowledge and experience in certain fields that can lead them into starting a small business in that field.  What these vets lack is the proper guidance and knowledge in starting a business such as developing a business plan, learning business and tax laws, basics of accounting, obtaining capital, how and where to buy products, internet and social media advertising, banking issues and generally just running a small business.  The founder of this corporation has operated several small businesses over 50 years and is now at the age where other vets can benefit from his knowledge and business experience in several fields.  With the guidance of the founder who has two current businesses, vets can begin working on a part-time or full-time basis and gain experience and knowledge of business requirements and later take over management and ownership of the businesses.  The founder also knows other small business owners close to retirement willing to train and assist vets to acquire their businesses.  Running this corporation on a for-profit basis ensures continued capital available to generate more opportunities for vets with potential.   A panel of small businessmen recruited by VETS USA will interview potential vets, then guide, train, encourage and assist them in developing their future plus provide some necessary start-up capital,   Experience has shown banks, SBA or other entities will not typically provide capital for a start-up business and certainly not provide any small business knowledge and experience.

Full Description: The United States essentially has one automotive restoration and engineering company that specializes in the restoration of Hollywood style vehicles.  That company is us. These customers are primarily interested in an already completed vehicle, not a vehicle built on contract (which is what we currently offer because we lack funds to produce the vehicles on a more efficient basis.)   Our marketing approach is simple; We utilize online resources to connect with potential buyers, while networking at large, high-dollar events such as Barrett-Jackson, and Mecum.  Our marketing has always been very successful and is an approach that we will continue to use. As mentioned above, our main issue is we don't have the funds available to appropriately build the vehicles up front, and sell them at high-dollar auctions (and to customers in general.)  When a vehicle is completed and doesn't have to be waited for, our profit increases $10,000-$30,000 per vehicle. At this time, our interest in obtaining cash flow to increase our efficiency, along with producing vehicles before the selling process.  We look forward to speaking further to you about the possibilities.

Description: Tradinguponline.com is an online social community that allows its users to trade up (swap) things things that they have no use for anymore
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Tradinguponline.com is an online social community that allows its users to trade up (swap) things "things that they have no use for anymore" with other users to get what they probably would like to have.  Let say you want something badly - for example a Sony PS3 console; but all you have is a fancy pen, perhaps given to you by an Uncle three years ago. Of course no one is going to trade PS3 for your pen. But what if someone has a PS3 and would like to exchange it for an X-Box. Some guy who's got an X-Box to trade wants to replace the carburetor in his car, and a lady whose father owns a  mechanic shop wouldn't mind asking daddy to spare one of those carburetors laying around the garage for her antique pen collection. So that leaves a trail for you to connect the dots. Start with something little - something you have, connect and trade it up until you find and get something you want. There is no selling of products between users, trades between users are practically Free!
